---
// Benefits.astro - Sección de beneficios del seguro de salud
---

<section id="beneficios" class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- Icono y título central -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <div
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-pacifico-blue rounded-full mb-6"
            >
                <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="32"
                    height="32"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    ><path
                        fill="white"
                        d="m12 20.3l-8.675-8.625q-.65-.65-.975-1.475q-.325-.825-.325-1.7q0-1.875 1.3-3.188Q4.625 4 6.5 4q.875 0 1.7.337q.825.338 1.475.988L12 7.625l2.325-2.3q.65-.65 1.475-.988Q16.625 4 17.5 4q1.875 0 3.188 1.312Q22 6.625 22 8.5q0 .875-.337 1.7q-.338.825-.988 1.475Zm-4.25-8.45l2.125-2.125l-2.3-2.275q-.25-.25-.538-.363Q6.75 6.975 6.475 7q-.6.025-1.037.462Q5 7.9 5 8.5q0 .275.113.55q.112.275.337.5Zm4.25 4.2l6.575-6.5q.225-.2.325-.488q.1-.287.1-.562q0-.6-.425-1.038Q18.15 7.025 17.55 7q-.275-.025-.562.087q-.288.113-.538.363l-6.55 6.5Z"
                    ></path></svg
                >
            </div>

            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
                Con un <span class="text-pacifico-blue"
                    >Seguro<br />de Salud</span
                >, podrás tener:
            </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Grid de beneficios -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <!-- Beneficio 1: Consultas médicas -->
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div
                    class="bg-pacifico-gray rounded-2xl p-8 h-64 flex flex-col items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-16 h-16 bg-pacifico-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="32"
                            height="32"
                            viewBox="0 0 15 15"
                        >
                            <path
                                fill="white"
                                d="M5.5 7A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 3 4.5v-2a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5H4a.5.5 0 0 0 0-1h-.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2 2.5v2a3.49 3.49 0 0 0 1.51 2.87A4.4 4.4 0 0 1 5 10.5a3.5 3.5 0 1 0 7 0v-.57a2 2 0 1 0-1 0v.57a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-5 0a4.4 4.4 0 0 1 1.5-3.13A3.49 3.49 0 0 0 9 4.5v-2A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 7.5 1H7a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v2A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 5.5 7m6 2a1 1 0 1 1 0-2a1 1 0 0 1 0 2"
                            ></path></svg
                        >
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                        Consultas médicas
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                        Acceso a médicos especialistas y consultas preventivas
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Beneficio 2: Emergencias -->
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div
                    class="bg-pacifico-gray rounded-2xl p-8 h-64 flex flex-col items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-400 to-red-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="32"
                            height="32"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                fill="white"
                                d="M12.692 11.077v-6.27q0-.347.23-.577T13.5 4h5.692q.349 0 .578.23t.23.578v3.538q0 .348-.23.578t-.578.23h-4.576zM18.931 20q-2.529 0-5.185-1.266t-4.944-3.555q-2.27-2.288-3.536-4.935T4 5.07q0-.45.3-.76T5.05 4h2.473q.408 0 .712.257t.411.659L9.142 7.3q.07.42-.025.733t-.333.513L6.59 10.592q.616 1.117 1.361 2.076t1.59 1.817q.87.87 1.874 1.62q1.004.749 2.204 1.414l2.139-2.177q.244-.263.549-.347q.304-.083.674-.033l2.103.43q.408.1.662.411t.254.712v2.435q0 .45-.31.75t-.76.3"
                            ></path></svg
                        >
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                        Atención de emergencias
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                        Cobertura 24/7 para situaciones de emergencia
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Beneficio 3: Hospitalización -->
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div
                    class="bg-pacifico-gray rounded-2xl p-8 h-64 flex flex-col items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-16 h-16 bg-pacifico-pink rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="32"
                            height="32"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                fill="white"
                                d="M10.5 13.5v2q0 .625.438 1.063T12 17t1.063-.437t.437-1.063v-2h2q.625 0 1.063-.437T17 12t-.437-1.062T15.5 10.5h-2v-2q0-.625-.437-1.062T12 7t-1.062.438T10.5 8.5v2h-2q-.625 0-1.062.438T7 12t.438 1.063T8.5 13.5zM5 21q-.825 0-1.412-.587T3 19V5q0-.825.588-1.412T5 3h14q.825 0 1.413.588T21 5v14q0 .825-.587 1.413T19 21zm0-2h14V5H5zM5 5v14z"
                            ></path></svg
                        >
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                        Hospitalización
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                        Cobertura completa para internamiento y cirugías
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Texto adicional -->
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
            <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Y muchos beneficios más que te ayudarán a mantener tu
                tranquilidad y la de tu familia ante cualquier eventualidad de
                salud.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
